                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-12 row mt-30">
                <div class="col-sm-4 mb-10">
                    <img src="~/Lib/images/dandimarket3/post_6.jpg" />
                </div>
                <div class="col-sm-4 mb-10">
                    <img src="~/Lib/images/dandimarket3/post_7.jpg" />
                </div>
                <div class="col-sm-4 mb-10">
                    <img src="~/Lib/images/dandimarket3/post_8.jpg" />
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
<!-- 셀러신청 -->
<section class="page-section dandi-section">
    <div class="container relative pt-40">
        <div class="col-sm-4">
            <div class="dandi-title mb-10">셀러 신청</div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-8">
            <div class="dandi-content align-left">
                자신만의 색깔을 가진 사람은 누구나 참여 가능한 단디마켓!
